{
  "stem": "1169.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That it's these 19 Polish Jews who stopped for a second to listen to the shofar that inspired me always to these feelings and thoughts that the Jewish nation has such a huge credit card up in heaven that, if for no other reason, but 19 Jews had the guts in 1944 to stop in Bergen-Belsen from their labors and listen to the shofar, that's enough credit before all the Heavenly authorities that the final redemption to the Jewish nation should come.",
      "word_count": 82
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] They have no more excuse to refrain, to withhold this blessing from the Jewish nation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They really suffered enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] We also had the secret holiday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And just for the Rabbi of Satmar, they took one of these three-tiered carts out into the yard and put on the top of it straw.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was his [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, the winds came, the rain came, blew it over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it lasted one day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there was even a semblance of this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] One night in December-- again, these things they always did at middle of the night, at 12:00 at night-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they come around.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We have to pack like at the time of deportation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We are going to be freed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was [NON-ENGLISH] holiday, I believe it was December 20th or 21st.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Again, be ready at 6:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we are going to be freed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They did not tell us where we are going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "OK, everyone puts their meager possessions together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we line up in the yard to be freed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Then they announce the railroad station, which is [INAUDIBLE], is very far away.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
